<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        
        .shop-info {
            margin: 1rem 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .actions {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            color: #dc2626;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .troubleshoot {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        
        .troubleshoot h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .troubleshoot ol {
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .troubleshoot li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 1rem;
                padding: 2rem;
            }
            
            .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
        <h1>Installation Error</h1>
        
        <% if (shop) { %>
            <div class="shop-info">
                <strong>Shop:</strong> <%= shop %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="error-message">
            <%= error %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn">
                üè† Back to Home
            </a>
            <a href="/auth/shopify?shop=<%= shop || 'your-shop' %>" class="btn btn-secondary">
                üîÑ Try Again
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="troubleshoot">
            <h3>üîß Troubleshooting Steps</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Check App Configuration:</strong> Ensure your Shopify app settings are correct in the Partner Dashboard</li>
                <li><strong>Verify URLs:</strong> Make sure the App URL and Redirect URLs match your deployed app</li>
                <li><strong>API Credentials:</strong> Confirm your API key and secret are properly set in environment variables</li>
                <li><strong>Development Store:</strong> If testing, make sure you're using a development store</li>
                <li><strong>Browser Issues:</strong> Try clearing browser cache or using an incognito window</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>